heart is full ❤️
I completed my final evaluation as a student of Canada’s National Ballet School this week and I couldn’t be prouder of my class. 
I would not be where I am without my dear teacher Vera Timashova and I am so thankful to be graduating surrounded by my inspiring “Tima Girls” ballet class. So much love for you all! 🫶🏻

❤️‍🔥“The Five Canticles” by James Kudelka 
with @elia_vvs_ballet

🖤 6.23.2023 🖤

As I leave Canada’s National Ballet School to embark on my new journey as a professional ballet dancer, I feel nothing but gratitude and love for everyone I encountered on my path. 
My fellow graduates brought love and laughter to our daily lives and we grew up together into talented individuals that I am proud to call family. 
This school has brought me such rich experiences and opportunities and I am so thankful to all the people along the way that contributed towards my development. 
I am most grateful for my teacher and mentors 🤍 
To the class of 2023, I love you all. You are amazing and I am so proud :) #graduation
